column1: ## This spreadsheet is used for including new TACT encryption keys that haven't yet been added to this client. They may allow you to load newer encrypted models.

## You can find a full list of TACT keys here: https://wowdev.wiki/TACT#TACT_keys or https://github.com/wowdev/TACTKeys (more up to date). Consult the page's history for keys that were added after this version of WMV was released.

column2: Key pairs should be added below. This file should be saved as a CSV spreadsheet with the cell divider as a *semicolon*, not a comma."
